HEADWORD: Narcotic
<hw>Nar*cot"ic</hw> <pr>(n⟦aum⟧r*k⟦ocr⟧t"⟦icr⟧k)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[F. <ets>narcotique</ets>, Gr. <grk>narkwtiko`s</grk>, fr.
<grk>narkoy^n</grk> to benumb, <grk>na`rkh</grk> numbness,
